			<div class="details">
				<h3>Guidelines</h3>
				<p>BSA Inspire seeks to fund long-term, lasting projects that benefit the Brown or Providence community. For this reason, we will not fund events - even if they are recurring.</p>
				<p>BSA will award up to $1,000 of reimbursable funding per project. If the project is seeking funding aside from BSA Inspire, applicants must disclose where else they will seek funding.</p>
				<p>At the end of each semester, we ask recepients to provide a documentation of their progress. This could be a video, photos with interviews, a blog maintained throughout the semester, or a similar project. This way, we can showcase your success and hopefully inspire other students.</p>
			</div>
