			<div class="details">
				<h3>Application Process</h3>
				<p>We offer five rounds of applications. In the fall, they are October 30th and November 30th. In the spring, they are February 28th, March 30th, and April 30th.</p>
				<p>There is no advantage to applying in fall versus spring but we recommend applying in the earlier rounds within either semester.</p>
				<p>Each person or group may only apply once per semester. If your application is rejected, you may reapply once more in the same semester.</p>
